      "file_path": "kubernetes/policy/charts/policy-apex-pdp/resources/config/config.json",
      "patchset_number": 4,
      "line": 22,
      "message": "I think Ross needs some direction here on how APEX sets the truststore and keystore password and cert store location must be set for apex, in order to do the right changes, it's very confusing.\n\nIs there any configuration that should go here?\n\nhttps://git.onap.org/oom/tree/kubernetes/policy/charts/policy-apex-pdp/resources/config/OnapPfConfig.json\n\nOr it is just in the image, and the location and password should be passed as environment variables?\n\nShould the passwords be base64 encoded or not?",
      "author": {
